{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "69344664-32a5-4546-9415-4a2d97121114", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/69344664-32a5-4546-9415-4a2d97121114@1.pkg/1772597617990/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597618686", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/69344664-32a5-4546-9415-4a2d97121114@1.pkg/1772597617990/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597618686"}, "identifier": "69344664-32a5-4546-9415-4a2d97121114", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①正确：神舟二十号载人飞船成功发射升空，展现我国科技城就，体现对发展有信心，国人感到自豪体现对国家有认同。</p>\n\n<p>③正确：《哪吒之魔童闹海》全球票房突破159亿元，中国优秀传统文化影响力扩大体现坚守文化立场，对文化有底气。</p>\n\n<p>②④不符合题意：材料观点没有体现。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025东华二模）以下是九年级（1）班“我眼中的自信中国人”活动的部分采访摘录，对以下观点理解正确的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"${ref-path}/edu/questions/image.png\">​</p>\n\n<p>①要对国家有认同，对发展有信心 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;②要满怀激情，坚定理论自信</p>\n\n<p>③要坚守文化立场，对文化有底气 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;④实现中国梦要坚持党的领导</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025东华二模）以下是九年级（1）班“我眼中的自信中国人”活动的部分采访摘录，对以下观点理解正确的是（   ）①要对国家有认同，对发展有信心      ②要满怀激情，坚定理论自信③要坚守文化立场，对文化有底气      ④实现中国梦要坚持党的领导", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/69344664-32a5-4546-9415-4a2d97121114@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754818676280", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "t